Class Open Errors

If Zelix KlassMaster detects errors within the classes that it has opened it reports the fact by displaying the "Class Open Errors" screen. Some obfuscators deliberately insert corrupt information into a class file in the hope of confusing or even crashing decompilers. Zelix KlassMaster removes corrupt Local Variable Table and Inner Class information automatically. Files that are totally corrupt are skipped.
